# Klauern Skills Project Overview

This is a Claude Code plugin marketplace repository containing custom skills that extend Claude's capabilities.

## Repository Structure

The project follows a modular structure where each skill is self-contained:

- **Skills Directory**: Each skill has its own directory at the root level
- **Command Files**: Slash commands are defined in the [`commands/`](mdc:commands/) directory
- **Marketplace Config**: Plugin definitions in [`.claude-plugin/marketplace.json`](mdc:.claude-plugin/marketplace.json)

## Main Entry Points

- **Repository README**: [`README.md`](mdc:README.md) - Installation instructions and overview
- **Conventional Commits Skill**: [`conventional-commits/SKILL.md`](mdc:conventional-commits/SKILL.md)
- **PR Creator Skill**: [`pr-creator/SKILL.md`](mdc:pr-creator/SKILL.md)

## Available Commands

- [`/commit`](mdc:commands/commit.md) - Create conventional commits without pushing
- [`/commit-push`](mdc:commands/commit-push.md) - Create conventional commits and push
- [`/pr`](mdc:commands/pr.md) - Create intelligent pull requests

