## Development Guidelines

When developing in this repository:

1. Each skill should be self-contained in its own directory
2. Skills must include a `SKILL.md` file with metadata and instructions
3. Commands go in the `commands/` directory as markdown files
4. Reference documentation goes in skill subdirectories
5. All skills must be registered in `.claude-plugin/marketplace.json`

## Installation Methods

Users can install skills via:

- Interactive: `/plugin` then search
- All plugins: `/plugin install conventional-commits@klauern-skills` and `/plugin install pr-creator@klauern-skills`
- Individual: `/plugin install conventional-commits@klauern-skills` or `/plugin install pr-creator@klauern-skills`
- Local dev: `/plugin add-marketplace /path/to/repo`
